reviewText:
I am mom of three so when I am shopping I am always looking for good deals and things that can last awhile. So for my son I am able to shop ahead seasons still so I bought this shirt in a six t and was amazed with this shirt. When it came in the package he had to try it on right away. He said he loved how it feels. He was so excited he wore it all night and he refused to take it off. I was also surprised by the brand when I got it home because it says it is PGXT Boys Babyboy Kids Cotton Long Sleeve Fake Two T Shirts Tees but it was actually a different brand instead. I am very happy with the brand that it was though it is a popular kids clothing brand.
