Again it runs true to size I believe but my son is small so I would always size up to be safe if so you can be having a shirt that will fit nicely. Plus with shrinkage you never know what it will end up after you wash it. I am very impressed with this shirt and would recommend it and so would my son! I have received a discount for my honest review. The opinions and statements are my own and are in no way biased because of said discount.
